[With the newly confirmed case in a healthcare worker in Hufoof (Hafuf, Hufof), it appears as the outbreak in Hufoof is continuing with apparent transmission in both in the healthcare environment and the community (perhaps in the extended household contacts of the earlier cases. There have now been 12 cases reported from Hufof since 20 Apr 2015, with today's case being the 1st reported case in a healthcare worker in this current outbreak.

The reported case fatality rate is now approaching 44 percent.

A map showing the locations of the cases in Saudi Arabia can be found at the source URLs. - Mod.MPP]

